      <title>花旗预测改革将保护尼日利亚奈拉免受油价下跌的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/nigeria-s-naira-usd-ngn-how-reforms-could-buffer-naira-from-oil-slump</link>
